     A                                      EDTCDE(4)
     A  13                                  DSPATR(PC RI)
     A            D1NONY         4  0B   + 4TEXT('DELIVERY CODE')
     A                                      DSPATR(CS) EDTCDE(4)
     A  14                                  DSPATR(PC RI)
      *
     A                                 10 18'0- CANCEL '
     A                                 11 18'1- CHANGE '
     A                                 12 18'2- ADD    '
      *
